    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, a specimen that reflects an uncompromising standard of care. This motorcar remains in impeccable condition, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of true showroom caliber. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the pristine interior cabin, serves as a testament to its meticulous history. Mechanically peerless and aesthetically unrivaled, this offering represents the zenith of its class.",
