    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019ve babied it from day one. Seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a scratch or a smudge anywhere! It\u2019s in truly pristine, showroom condition, and I\u2019m only letting it go because I\u2019m looking for something a bit bigger for the family. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
